Package: nciusual
Title: NCI Method for Estimating Usual Dietary Intake Distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Conor", "McGovern", email = "comcgovern@example.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R port of the National Cancer Institute (NCI) MIXTRAN and DISTRIB
    SAS macros for estimating usual dietary intake distributions from 24-hour
    dietary recall data. Supports amount-only models (for ubiquitously consumed
    nutrients) and two-part correlated/uncorrelated models (for episodically
    consumed foods). Designed for use with NHANES data and complex survey designs.
